wine.name: Wine
wine.title: Veuve Monsigny Champagne Brut
wine.ingredients: A bestseller and highly acclaimed award-winner from the small, consistently excellent Champagne house Philizot & Fils. This blend of Chardonnay, Pinot Noir and Pinot Meunier has been aged in cellars to enhance its complexity, elegance and length.
wine.orderText: You order Wine Veuve Monsigny Champagne Brut, amount of 4 pieces, price: 680 UAH.

wine.name: Wine
wine.title: Organic Prosecco
wine.ingredients: Eco-friendly fizz sourced from the Corvezzo family’s 150-hectare estate, 30km north-east of Venice. Grown with no pesticides or herbicides used in the vineyard, the grapes are predominately hand picked and gently pressed to ensure only the highest quality of juice is used. The winery is also committed to using renewable energy wherever possible.

wine.name: Wine
wine.title: Blanc De Blanc
wine.ingredients: A pale gold colour, with a well balanced and persistent perlange. This Castellore Vino Spumante has an inviting aroma with hints of citrus fruits and flowers. Serve at 6-8 degrees with appetizers, fish and seafood dishes or desserts and confectionery.

wine.name: Wine
wine.title: Rosé-Spumante
wine.ingredients: A classic and elegant Italian rosé sparkling wine, with intense summer fruits, pears and citrus freshness. Delicious served chilled as an apéritif.

wine.name: Wine
wine.title: Exquisite Clare Valley Riesling
wine.ingredients: An exceptional dry Riesling showing a characteristic steeliness to the green apple, lime and grapefruit notes. Citrus softens to subtle tangerine and the refreshing minerality creates a sustained and mouth-watering finish. Delicious with seafood, mild Chinese and Thai dishes, or salads.

wine.name: Wine
wine.title: Marlborough Sauvignon
wine.ingredients: Complex aromas of white stone fruits and blackcurrant leaf give way to flavours of lime-drizzled nectarine and an intriguingly soft texture, with a long and thoughtful finish.
